# LapseIQ root .dockerignore — Sprint 5 (B2)
#
# Applies when a build is run from the REPO ROOT context (e.g.
# `docker build .` or a future top-level Dockerfile). The per-stack
# build contexts (./server and ./client used by docker-compose.yml)
# each carry their own .dockerignore tailored to their tree.
#
# Two reasons this file exists:
#   1. Secrets — a stray .env or credential file in the build context
#      can end up in an image layer if a Dockerfile ever does `COPY . .`.
#   2. Image size + cache invalidation — node_modules and uploads/
#      both thrash Docker's layer cache and bloat the final image.

# ── Secrets and credentials (NEVER ship) ─────────────────────────────────────
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development
**/.env.production
**/.env.*.local
**/secrets/
**/.aws/
**/.ssh/
**/credentials.json

# ── Runtime data (must come from bind mounts, not layers) ────────────────────
**/uploads/
**/backups/

# ── Build artefacts and dependencies (regenerated inside the image) ──────────
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/coverage/
**/.cache/
**/.parcel-cache/
**/.vite/
**/.prisma/

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# ── Stray scratch files (must never ship) ────────────────────────────────────
server/_check_user.js
server/_reset_pw.js
server/p.$disconnect())
server/check.js

# ── Source control / IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github
.vscode
.idea
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Tests and docs that bloat the image ──────────────────────────────────────
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.js
**/__tests__/
**/test/
**/tests/
docs/
ROADMAP.md
# (NEXT_SESSION.md and UX_REVIEW_*.md patterns retired 2026-05-10: those
# files now land under docs/sessions/YYYY-MM-DD/ per docs/CONVENTIONS.md,
# which is already covered by the docs/ exclude above.)
